data.title: Redpoint Ventures
data.meta_description: Redpoint partners with visionary entrepreneurs to create new markets & redefine existing ones. We invest in startups across seed, early & growth phases.
data.text:
Railway is the cloud that takes the complexity out of shipping software.

We first invested in Railway's Series A in 2022.

Guild is pioneering an approach to Education as a Benefit, helping companies transform traditional tuition assistance programs from a cost center into a recruitment and retention tool.

We first partnered for their Series A in 2016.

Ramp is the finance automation platform designed to save you time and money.

Redpoint invested in the Series B in 2021.

Snowflake is a SaaS-based cloud data warehousing platform designed to safely and efficiently store, transform, and analyze business data.

We partnered for their Series B in 2014, through their IPO in September 2020.

Nubank is challenging the status quo to create a new generation of financial services in Latin America.

We first partnered for their Series D in 2016.

Cityblock partners with health plans to reach people in neighborhoods that face high poverty rates and accompanying social challenges.

We partnered for their Series B in 2019.

MotherDuck is on a mission to combine the elegance and speed of DuckDB with the collaboration and scalability of the cloud to provide a serverless, easy to use analytics platform for data small and large.

Redpoint first invested in the seed in 2022.

Powerful, flexible and data-driven, Attio makes it easy to build the exact CRM your business needs.

We first partnered with Attio on their Series A.

Foundry is a new breed of public cloud, powered by an orchestration platform that makes accessing AI compute as easy as flipping a light switch.

We first partnered at the Series A.

Trained from scratch like all Ideogram models, Ideogram 1.0 offers state-of-the-art text rendering, unprecedented photorealism and prompt adherence, and a new feature called Magic Prompt that helps you write detailed prompts for beautiful, creative images.

Scribe is a simple, effective way for anyone to share knowledge at work or home without burdening creators or viewers.

We first partnered with Scribe for their Series B in 2024.

GreenPlaces is the all-in-one sustainability platform empowers businesses of all sizes to meet their goals–from carbon reporting, to emission reductions, to measurable ROI.

Omni is the only BI platform that combines the consistency of a shared data model with the freedom of SQL

DragonflyDB is rethinking what an in-memory datastore should look and behave like, with the goal of building something significantly more performant and easier to scale than Redis.

Their goal is to redesign the engine using novel algorithms and data structures, innovating around lockless multithreading, memory structures, caching algorithms, and snapshotting to provide a simple, cost-efficient, and reliable in-memory store that delights the engineering community.

Powerful, flexible and data-driven, Attio makes it easy to build the exact CRM your business needs.
